  <lyrics>[V1]
 Cristot jayán jacáyáta,
 Juchanacans phokfata,
 Ucat Cristoruw arfasta,
 Jupajj perdonjjetuwa.
 
[C]
 Jichhasti yuspagarsmawa,
 Nayaru khespiyatamat.
 Jucha jjsa k'omachistawa,
 Jumar sirviñataqui.
 
[V2]
 Lup'itajjas, parlatajjas,
 Jumar uw fiankhachána,
 Suma k'oma wilamampiw,
 Nayar k'omachfasjjesta.
 
[V3]
 Jumatejj Tatit Cristoru,
 Jucham arsusismajja,
 Khespiyataw uñjasisma,
 Take juchanacata.
 
</lyrics></song>